<span id="freeTextContainer14083358652276302058"><a href='https://ibb.co/tc7Vz7Q' rel='nofollow noopener'>
  <img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1578819018i/28762032._SX540_.jpg' alt='opal' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/>
</a><br/><br/>This series has consumed me! I&apos;ve never read so quick, I can&apos;t convey how much I&apos;ve loved what I&apos;ve read so far, I&apos;ve been devouring the pages, and because sleep is overrated my time has been better spent reading/inhaling books 1&amp;2 in record speeds!! I never read this quick!! <br/>My ass is numb, I&apos;m hungry, my eyes are tired, my brain is fried, BUT for the life of me I couldn&apos;t put this down, god the partner wanted us to go out and I made some excuse!! #DEAD!!<br/><br/>My heart missed beats, my palms got </span>
  <span id="freeText14083358652276302058" style="display:none"><a href="https://ibb.co/tc7Vz7Q" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1578819018i/28762032._SX540_.jpg" alt="opal" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br>This series has consumed me! I've never read so quick, I can't convey how much I've loved what I've read so far, I've been devouring the pages, and because sleep is overrated my time has been better spent reading/inhaling books 1&amp;2 in record speeds!! I never read this quick!! <br>My ass is numb, I'm hungry, my eyes are tired, my brain is fried, BUT for the life of me I couldn't put this down, god the partner wanted us to go out and I made some excuse!! #DEAD!!<br><br>My heart missed beats, my palms got sweaty, my nails are bitten, what an amazing ride this one has been!! This was slow to start but then that burn kicked in and I was loving every second, minture, hours I spent reading this! <br><br>Yet again this author has pulled that <b>5+++++</b> star rating out of me effortlessly!!<br><br>Holy crap I'm so glad I don't have too long to wait until I get to the next book, one arc and then onto the next book!! I have to/need to finish this series..That cliffy was brutal, one I never saw coming!!<br><br>And yet again if you've not read this series and like me it's been sitting on your device collecting dust seriously get reading, it's that good!!<br><br><blockquote>
