			<a class="actionLink" href="/topic/show/16907085-opal-lux-3-by-jennifer-l-armentrout---restarting-october-21st-2021">Opal ( Lux #3 ) by Jennifer L. Armentrout - Restarting October 21st 2021</a>
		</td>
